{
  "chapter": 12,
  "chapter_summary": "楚留香与石绣云在众人刻意回避后独处一室，相对饮酒。石绣云主动邀酒赌气连饮，渐露醉意后撒娇让楚留香替她穿鞋，二人漫步至初见时的木屋共度一夜。次日清晨，石绣云却洒脱告别，表示满足于这一日甜蜜回忆，绝不会纠缠楚留香，令楚留香怅然若失。胡铁花忽然到访，一反常态情绪低落自嘲。楚留香追问得知高亚男对他视而不见，而华山派掌门枯梅大师竟已还俗下山，身穿花袍俨然诰命夫人，此事必有重大隐情。楚留香决意陪胡铁花查探这件蹊跷大事。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "石绣云",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你不敬我酒?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "text": "你会喝酒?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "石绣云",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你若敢跟我拼酒，我一定把你灌醉。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "text": "好，我敬你一杯。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "石绣云",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "多小气，要敬就敬三杯，你……你怕我会喝醉?",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "text": "老实说，我倒真未想到你会喝酒，而且酒量还不错。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "石绣云",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "怎么，你看我像是乡下人，是不是?告诉你，乡下人也会喝酒的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "石绣云",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "再告诉你，今年过年的时候，我一个人就喝了一坛，你信不信?",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "text": "如此说来，我倒真该找小胡来跟你喝酒才是。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "石绣云",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "小胡是谁?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "text": "他叫胡铁花，是我的老朋友，也是我的好朋友，他的酒量比我强得多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "石绣云",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "好，下次你把他找来，我把他灌醉给你看，可是今天……今天……我却只要跟你喝酒。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "石绣云",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "来，我敬你。你敬我三杯，我敬你六杯，我的气派比你大多了吧?",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "text": "六杯?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "石绣云",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "六杯，你嫌少?还是嫌多了?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "text": "好像是多了些。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "石绣云",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "怎么，你怕我喝醉是不是?只要你自己不醉就好了，莫管我。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "text": "我喝完了这六杯，就送你回去好不好?",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "石绣云",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你……你先喝完再说。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "石绣云",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我不回去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "text": "你……你不回去?为什么?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "石绣云",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "没有为什么，我就是不想回去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "石绣云",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "来，现在该轮到你敬我酒了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "石绣云",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我的心情不好，我想喝酒，你难道就不肯陪陪我?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "text": "只要你不喝醉，我陪你喝三天都没关系。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "石绣云",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你怕我喝醉?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "text": "谁喝醉我都怕，我什么都不怕，就怕喝醉酒的人。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "石绣云",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我保证绝不喝醉，行不行?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "text": "好，我敬你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "石绣云",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你不是好人，我早就知道你不是好人……我第一次看见你的时候，就知道我要倒楣了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "text": "我哪点不好?",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "石绣云",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你把我灌醉了……你把我灌醉了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "text": "你不是说你不会醉的吗?",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "石绣云",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这么闷，闷死人，陪我出去走走好不好。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "text": "好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "石绣云",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我的鞋……我的鞋子呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "石绣云",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你替我穿上……你不替我穿上，我就不走。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "石绣云",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你可知道我为什么要到这里来?",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "石绣云",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "因为这是我第一眼看到你的地方。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "text": "走吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "石绣云",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "走?为什么要走?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "text": "你若再不走，可知道我会怎么样?",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "text": "你既已知道我不是好人，你就该猜得出我要做什么事，你快些走是你的运气，否则我就要撕破你的衣服，然后……",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "石绣云",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你真坏，坏死了，我就知道你总有一天会这样对我的。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "石绣云",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你摸摸我身上是不是在发烧?",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "石绣云",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你这个坏东西，你一直在勾引我，从头到尾都在勾引我，你以为我不知道?现在你又要逃了，你若敢逃走，小心我咬断你的手指。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "石绣云",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我的头好疼。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "text": "想到第二天的头疼，以后你总该少喝些酒了吧。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "石绣云",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我听说爱喝酒的人记性都不好，过两天就会将酒醉后的难受忘得干干净净了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "text": "一点也不错，据我所知，小胡至少已经戒了一千次酒了，每次头疼时他都嚷着要戒酒，可是不到半天就开了戒。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "石绣云",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "原来太阳已升得这么高了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "text": "时候的确已不早，我……我实在不想走……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "石绣云",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你不想走，我却要走了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "text": "你……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "石绣云",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我知道你也该走了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "text": "那么……那么以后我们……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "石绣云",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "以后?我们没有以后，因为以后你一定再也见不着我。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "石绣云",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你为什么吃惊?你难道以为我会缠住你，不放你走?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "石绣云",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我和你根本就不是一个世界里的人，我就算能勉强留住你，或者一定要跟你走，以后也不会幸福的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "石绣云",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我是个很平凡的人，以前一直过着平凡的日子，以后过的也一定是很平凡的日子，在我这一生中，能够跟你有这么样不平凡的一天……只要一天，我已很满足了，以后到我很老的时候，至少我还有这么一天甜蜜的回忆。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xiu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "石绣云",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "所以我无论如何都该感激你。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "小胡，你怎么会找到这里来了?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "老臭虫，你实在有两手……你是用什么法子将那女孩子骗得肯乖乖走了的?这法子你一定得教教我。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我何必教你，反正女孩子一看到你就逃得比马还快。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不错，你说的一点也不错，我是个酒鬼，又是个穷光蛋，又懒、又脏、又丑，若有女孩子见了我不逃，那才是怪事。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "谁会说你丑，那人眼睛一定瞎了，你看你的鼻子、眉毛、眼睛……尤其是你这双眼睛，一万个男人中也找不出一个。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "就算我眼睛长得还不错也没有用，我是个穷光蛋。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "男子汉大丈夫，穷一点有什么关系，只要你穷得骨头硬……世上的女孩子并非个个都是见钱眼开的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "只可惜我又是个酒鬼。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 359
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "喝酒又有什么不好?喝酒的人才有男子气概，古来有名的英雄、将相、诗人，哪个不喝酒，女孩子见到你喝酒的豪气，一颗心早已掉在你酒杯里了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "莫非你又见着高亚男了?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "她难道还不理你?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "她……她就是不理我，简直就好像不认得我这个人似的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "这到底是怎么回事，你仔细说给我听听。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "有一天我得了两坛好酒，就去找\"快网\"张三，因为他烤的鱼最好，我记得你也很爱吃的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "不错，只有他烤的鱼，不腥不老，又不失鱼的鲜味。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我和他正坐在船头烤鱼吃酒，忽然有条船很快的从我们旁边过去，船上有三个人，其中有个我觉得很面熟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "高亚男?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "那时我也大吃一惊，就追下去，想跟她打个招呼，谁知她根本不理我，我拼命向她招手，她就像没瞧见。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "也许……也许她真的没有看到你。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 411
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "谁说的?她就坐在窗口，眼睛瞪了我半天，却像是瞪着根木头似的，我一路追下去，她一路坐在窗口，可就是不理我。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你为什么不索性跳上她的船?去问个明白。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 417
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我不敢。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你不敢?为什么?她顶多也不过只能把你踢下船而已。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "因为她的师父，华山派的那老尼姑也在船上，我倒真有点怕……我不是怕她别的，就怕她那张脸。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "枯梅大师已有二十余年未履红尘，这一次怎会下山来了?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 431
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你莫难受，等我这里的事办完了，就陪你去找她，问问她为何不理你?",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 435
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你见了枯梅大师，一定也会大吃一惊的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 437
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "因为她已还俗了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "枯梅大师会还俗!你见了鬼吧。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我也知道这件事无论说给谁听，都绝没有人会相信，但她的的确确是还俗了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你只怕是看错人了吧。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "枯梅大师的容貌，任何人看了一眼都不会忘记，何况是我?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 455
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我见着她时，她穿的是件紫缎团花的花袍，手里扶着根龙头拐杖，头上白发苍苍，看来就像是位子孙满堂的诰命夫人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你在这里等我，午时前后，我一定回来陪你去。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 470
    }
  ],
